      • getOrderType

        public java.lang.String getOrderType()
        Returns:
        orderType The type of bet (e.g standard limited-liability Exchange bet (LIMIT), a standard BSP bet (MARKET_ON_CLOSE), or a minimum-accepted-price BSP bet (LIMIT_ON_CLOSE)). If the bet has a OrderType of MARKET_ON_CLOSE and a persistenceType of MARKET_ON_CLOSE then it is a bet which has transitioned from LIMIT to MARKET_ON_CLOSE. Only available at BET groupBy level.
